  "vulnerability_information": "HTTP OPTIONS method is enabled on this web server. The OPTIONS method provides a list of the methods that are supported by the web server, it represents a request for information about the communication options available on the request/response chain identified by the Request-URI.\n\nDomain :\nmerchant.kartpay.com\n\n## Impact\n\nThe issue was not critical, as the impact of using other methods than GET and POST in this domain is nearly nonexistent. The bounty reflects the criticality of the issue.",
